Kahless is the legendary first Klingon Emperor, who united the Klingon people. There are two versions of his title. The older version, {qeylIS lIjlaHbogh pagh:n:name@@qeylIS:n, lIj:v, -laH:v, -bogh:v, pagh:n:1}, is applied to Kahless only, while the newer version {qeylIS'e' lIjlaHbe'bogh vay':n:name,nolink} may be applied to Kahless and other leaders/heroes as well. It would be a sign of extreme arrogance or disrespect to use the older version for anyone other than Kahless.[2]

His return is prophesied in the Story of the Promise, which states that:
